    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Webhook receptor de leads y notificador Telegram\n**Trigger: POST desde Thunder Client o cualquier cliente HTTP\nProcesa: nombre y email del body\nManeja: campos faltantes con optional chaining + fallback\nResponde: JSON procesado al emisor\nTest: Thunder Client → Body JSON → Execute workflow activo\nPropósito: capturar leads de pablocuevas.it, enriquecerlos con validación de email y notificar en tiempo real.",
        "height": 352,
        "width": 304
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        -1008,
        -16
      ],
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "id": "1a2f6c55-2928-43a8-9ee8-04fb63f47def",
      "name": "Sticky Note4"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const item = $input.all()[0];\nconst body = item.json.body || item.json;\n\nconst dominiosGratuitos = [\"gmail.com\", \"hotmail.com\", \"yahoo.com\", \"outlook.com\", \"libero.it\", \"virgilio.it\"];\n\nconst email = body.email?.toLowerCase().trim() || null;\nconst dominio = email?.split(\"@\")[1] || null;\nconst prioridad = !dominio ? \"no especificada\" \n  : dominiosGratuitos.includes(dominio) ? \"baja\" \n  : \"alta\";\n\nconst timestamp = new Date().toLocaleString(\"it-IT\", { timeZone: \"Europe/Rome\" });\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    nome: body.nome || \"sconosciuto\",\n    cognome: body.cognome || \"\",\n    email: email,\n    azienda: body.azienda || \"non specificata\",\n    servizio: body.servizio || \"non specificato\",\n    messaggio: body.messaggio || \"\",\n    prioridad: prioridad,\n    dominio: dominio,\n    timestamp_roma: timestamp,\n    procesado: true\n  }\n}];"
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        1376,
        64
      ],
      "id": "5e4f673e-ba8d-4727-aab2-2635684b7b3c",
      "name": "procesador-body1"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "##Abstract Email Reputation API\n**\n- Auth: Query Auth (api_key como query param — proveedor no soporta header)\n- Endpoint: GET https://emailreputation.abstractapi.com/v1/\n- Params: api_key (vault), email (dinámico)\n- Output: entregable, esEmailLibre, esDesechable, tipoCuenta, nivelRiesgo, accion_recomendada, razon\n- Campos descartados: email_sender.first/last_name (PII sin propósito), email_domain.domain (redundante), email_breaches (no relevante para clasificación)\n- Criterio accion_recomendada: descartar (desechable/no entregable/riesgo alto) → revisar_manualmente (riesgo medio o personal+libre) → procesar (resto)",
        "height": 384,
        "width": 368
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        192,
        -752
      ],
      "id": "4a9cbdc0-8de9-450d-ae8e-9962835271a0",
      "name": "Sticky Note6"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "url": "https://emailreputation.abstractapi.com/v1/",
        "authentication": "genericCredentialType",
        "genericAuthType": "httpQueryAuth",
        "sendQuery": true,
        "queryParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "email",
              "value": "={{ $('procesador-body1').item.json.email }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.4,
      "position": [
        1552,
